narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: You will work with some of the best singers to encounter in an educational vocal program.

The voice lesson program was an absolute gift for me. Never before has a class impacted my life so drastically. Scott Mello changed my voice in ways that I could never have imagined, and he created in me a deep interest in singing that I do not believe will ever go away.
Voice lessons for credit. If you sing, it's a sweet deal.
Great class, very little explanation needed. You take weekly lessons and get credit. Juries are not stressful and the community of teachers and students is great.
